Package tss

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArcherEntry
    ArcherEntry objects are used for filling the archers TableView element.
    Archers
    Utility class containing methods to do with creating, retrieving and updating archer data.
    DashboardController
    Controller class for mediating between the Dashboard GUI view and the system's model classes.
    MarriedCouples
    Utility class containing methods to do with creating, retrieving and updating married couple data.
    Results
    Utility class for generating the reports of the results for Individuals, Teams and Married Couples.
    ScoreEntry
    ScoreEntry objects are used for filling the tbvScores TableView element.
    Scores
    Utility class containing methods to do with creating, retrieving and updating score data.
    SQLiteConnection
    Utility class for connecting to the SQLite database used by the system.
    TargetEntry
    TargetEntry objects are used to fill the tbvTargetList TableView element.
    Targets  
    Team
    Team objects are used during the calculation of the team results, to rank the teams in descending order based on their scoring data.
    TeamMember
    TeamMember objects are Java Beans used to fill the data in the team results report generated by JasperReports.
    TournamentMap
    Custom Map class used to map tournament names to their tournament ID's
    Tournaments
    Utility class containing methods to do with creating, retrieving and updating tournament data.
    Validation
    Validation utility class that contains methods for various validation checks.
